official_title: Online Randomized Experiment Evaluating the Perceived Effectiveness of Alcohol Warning Labels
inclusion_criteria:
* Age 21 and older
* Reside in the United States
* Able to complete a survey in English
* Consumed alcohol at least once per week during the past 4 weeks
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 21 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Under the age of 21
* Reside outside of the United States
* Unable to complete a survey in English
* Consumed alcohol less than once per week during the past 4 weeks
